    <item>
      <title>Pre-Installation</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/docs/installation/pre-installation/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 12:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/docs/installation/pre-installation/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;pre-installation&#34;&gt;Pre-Installation &lt;a href=&#34;#pre-installation&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;material-icons align-middle&#34;&gt;link&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h4 id=&#34;preparation--research&#34;&gt;Preparation &amp;amp; Research &lt;a href=&#34;#preparation--research&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;material-icons align-middle&#34;&gt;link&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Review the &lt;a href=&#34;https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Installation_guide&#34; rel=&#34;external&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Arch Linux Installation Guide&lt;svg width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; d=&#34;M14 5c-.552 0-1-.448-1-1s.448-1 1-1h6c.552 0 1 .448 1 1v6c0 .552-.448 1-1 1s-1-.448-1-1v-3.586l-7.293 7.293c-.391.39-1.024.39-1.414 0-.391-.391-.391-1.024 0-1.414l7.293-7.293h-3.586zm-9 2c-.552 0-1 .448-1 1v11c0 .552.448 1 1 1h11c.552 0 1-.448 1-1v-4.563c0-.552.448-1 1-1s1 .448 1 1v4.563c0 1.657-1.343 3-3 3h-11c-1.657 0-3-1.343-3-3v-11c0-1.657 1.343-3 3-3h4.563c.552 0 1 .448 1 1s-.448 1-1 1h-4.563z&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for a detailed walkthrough.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Backup any important data (recommended if working on a non empty storage).&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Download the latest Arch Linux ISO from the official &lt;a href=&#34;https://archlinux.org/download/#download-mirrors&#34; rel=&#34;external&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Arch Linux website&lt;svg width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; d=&#34;M14 5c-.552 0-1-.448-1-1s.448-1 1-1h6c.552 0 1 .448 1 1v6c0 .552-.448 1-1 1s-1-.448-1-1v-3.586l-7.293 7.293c-.391.39-1.024.39-1.414 0-.391-.391-.391-1.024 0-1.414l7.293-7.293h-3.586zm-9 2c-.552 0-1 .448-1 1v11c0 .552.448 1 1 1h11c.552 0 1-.448 1-1v-4.563c0-.552.448-1 1-1s1 .448 1 1v4.563c0 1.657-1.343 3-3 3h-11c-1.657 0-3-1.343-3-3v-11c0-1.657 1.343-3 3-3h4.563c.552 0 1 .448 1 1s-.448 1-1 1h-4.563z&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;create-bootable-media&#34;&gt;Create Bootable Media &lt;a href=&#34;#create-bootable-media&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;material-icons align-middle&#34;&gt;link&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;Use tools such as &lt;a href=&#34;https://etcher.balena.io/&#34; rel=&#34;external&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Balena Etcher&lt;svg width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; d=&#34;M14 5c-.552 0-1-.448-1-1s.448-1 1-1h6c.552 0 1 .448 1 1v6c0 .552-.448 1-1 1s-1-.448-1-1v-3.586l-7.293 7.293c-.391.39-1.024.39-1.414 0-.391-.391-.391-1.024 0-1.414l7.293-7.293h-3.586zm-9 2c-.552 0-1 .448-1 1v11c0 .552.448 1 1 1h11c.552 0 1-.448 1-1v-4.563c0-.552.448-1 1-1s1 .448 1 1v4.563c0 1.657-1.343 3-3 3h-11c-1.657 0-3-1.343-3-3v-11c0-1.657 1.343-3 3-3h4.563c.552 0 1 .448 1 1s-.448 1-1 1h-4.563z&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.ventoy.net/en/index.html&#34; rel=&#34;external&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Ventoy&lt;svg width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; d=&#34;M14 5c-.552 0-1-.448-1-1s.448-1 1-1h6c.552 0 1 .448 1 1v6c0 .552-.448 1-1 1s-1-.448-1-1v-3.586l-7.293 7.293c-.391.39-1.024.39-1.414 0-.391-.391-.391-1.024 0-1.414l7.293-7.293h-3.586zm-9 2c-.552 0-1 .448-1 1v11c0 .552.448 1 1 1h11c.552 0 1-.448 1-1v-4.563c0-.552.448-1 1-1s1 .448 1 1v4.563c0 1.657-1.343 3-3 3h-11c-1.657 0-3-1.343-3-3v-11c0-1.657 1.343-3 3-3h4.563c.552 0 1 .448 1 1s-.448 1-1 1h-4.563z&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, or, if you prefer the command line, the &lt;code&gt;dd&lt;/code&gt; utility to write the ISO to a USB drive.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
